-Easter eggs
-Presentation
-And more

## In a paragraph or more, outline your next steps. What new skills will you need to acquire? What topics will you need to research? If working with one of two classmates, who will do what?
The new skills we need to acquire is how to program and code a game from scratch, but the concept of the game is non-original. Topics that may be included in our research are: Game engines, simple AI, incorporating textures, creating nodes, creating characters, and assigning functions to them. We will have to find and allocate the time to create our game. The skills we will be learning will be mostly new things, although we will be able to incorporate what we learned to translate over to our game. Finding the per Caohoc will be doing the design of characters and coding character movements. I will be coding the towers, upgrades, and try to code a simple ai. We plan to make ourselves do more as we progress more into the development of our game. Currently still in the brainstorming phase.
